 15-year-old person, climbed onto a freight carriage in a freight yard in Prenzlauer Berg. Three other people who were with him heard a loud bang and a flash of light. The 15 year-old received an electric shock from overhead power lines and was killed. To bring further meaning as to what happened that night, the Berlin Zeitung quotes an investigator as saying ''\"Apparently, in order to check the situation in the S-Bahn sweeping system, the 15-year-old climbed onto a parked car,\"''.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://archiv.berliner-zeitung.de/berlin/15-jaehriger-stirbt-durch-stromschlag-der-tote-graffiti-sprayer-auf-dem-gueterbahnhof-4468610|title=15-year-old dies from electric shock The dead graffiti sprayer at the freight station|date=27 December 2013|work=Berliner Zeitung|access-date=11 January 2020}}</ref> MAZ Online gives a report that expands further  along the relation between climbing up onto the freight car and the neighbouring S-Bahn train yard; ''\"The death of a 15-year-old at a Berlin freight station may have been an accident in the sprayer scene. As the \" Berliner Zeitung \" reports, referring to the investigators, the young people probably wanted to explore the area on Storkower Allee in order to spray graffiti on the S-Bahn trains parked there. A police spokesman did not want to confirm this suspicion, referring to the ongoing investigation. However, there is at least some evidence on the internet that the 15-year-old was actually active in the sprayer scene.\n''So there is a picture of December 24 on his Facebook profile , where several people in Santa Claus costumes spray a train wagon. On another Facebook page that was created to commemorate him , there is a photo of a graffiti that is said to have come from the 15-year-old.''\"''<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.maz-online.de/Brandenburg/Stromschlag-Tod-Hinweise-auf-Sprayer-Szene|title=electrocution death: references to sprayer scene|date=29 December 2013|work=Maz Online|access-date=11 January 2020}}</ref> \n<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.maz-online.de/Brandenburg/Stromschlag-Tod-Hinweise-auf-Sprayer-Szene|title=electrocution death: references to sprayer scene|date=29 December 2013|work=Maz Online|access-date=11 January 2020}}</ref>\n<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://archiv.berliner-zeitung.de/berlin/15-jaehriger-stirbt-durch-stromschlag-der-tote-graffiti-sprayer-auf-dem-gueterbahnhof-4468610|title=15-year-old dies from electric shock The dead graffiti sprayer at the freight station|date=27 December 2013|work=Berliner Zeitung|access-date=11 January 2020}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.berliner-kurier.de/berlin/polizei-und-justiz/15-000-volt---ramon--15--stirbt--durch-stromschlag-3961940|title=15,000 volts! Ramon (15) dies from electric shock|last=Oberst|first=Klaus|last2=Lehrke|first2=Gerhard|last3=Golling|first3=Anna|date=27 December 2013|work=Berliner Kurier|access-date=11 January 2020}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.tagesspiegel.de/berlin/polizei-justiz/berlin-prenzlauer-berg-kriminalpolizei-rekonstruiert-toedlichen-unfall-auf-gueterbahnhof/9263840.html|title=criminal police reconstructs fatal accident at freight yard|date=27 December 2013|work=Der Tagesspiegel|access-date=11 January 2020}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.nordkurier.de/aus-aller-welt/15-jaehriger-stirbt-auf-gueterbahnhof-durch-stromschlag-273999212.html|title=15-year-old dies of electric shock at freight station|date=27 December 2013|work=Nordkurier|access-date=11 January 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{dts|17 March 2014}}\n|France - Paris\n|Hit by object\n|20\n|A person, 20 was killed when they leaned out of a train window to spray graffiti on the outside of the train. As the train entered a tunnel they were hit by the entrance to the tunnel. Next to where the person was found was a bag containing spray paint cans.\n<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.leparisien.fr/amp/paris-75/rer-a-en-etat-de-mort-cerebrale-apres-avoir-passe-la-tete-hors-du-train-18-03-2014-3684435.php|title=RER A: brain dead after having put your head off the train|date=18 March 2014|work=leParisien|access-date=8 January 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{dts|02 July 2014}}\n|United States - New York\n|Electrocution\n|42\n|A 42-year-old person, who went by the tag \"DG\", died when he was electrocuted by the live third rail. He was found dead and alone, lying on the train tracks. Reports are uncertain as to what Jason's intentions where for being in the train tunnel. Sources reported that he had been heading back to where he lived in Queens, New York, and that it was possible he may have been tagging or intending to tag the tunnel.\n<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://news.artnet.com/art-world/nyc-graffiti-artist-dies-electrocuted-by-subways-third-rail-56852|title=NYC Graffiti Artist Dies Electrocuted by Subway\u2019s Third Rail|last=Cascone|first=Sarah|date=3 November 2014|work=artnet|access-date=30 December 2019}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://gothamist.com/news/graffiti-artist-electrocuted-by-third-rail-in-brooklyn#comments|title=Graffiti Artist Electrocuted By Third Rail In Brooklyn|last=Yakas|first=Ben|date=5 July 2014|work=Gothamist|access-date=30 December 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191229211133/https://gothamist.com/news/graffiti-artist-electrocuted-by-third-rail-in-brooklyn#comments|archive-date=29 December 2019|url-status=dead}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://nypost.com/2014/07/05/graffiti-legend-dies-in-subway-third-rail-electrocution/|title=Graffiti legend dies in subway third-rail electrocution|last=Harshbarger|first=Rebecca|date=5 July 2014|work=New York Post|access-date=30 December 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{dts|2014}}\n|Germany - Hamburg\n|Electrocuted by arc\n|21\n|In autumn 2014, Julius Gerhardt, 21, was with some people spraying freight carriages. Gerhardt climbed on top of a freight car and was intending to tag a bridge. He was holding a spray can in his right hand. An electric arc jumped over to the spray can and went through his hand, arm, chest, then exited out his right right foot. Gerhardt lost consciousness and was then lifted up by the people with him and carried to a street. He was in a coma in hospital for 36 hours and then later he was put into a medically induced coma for a week. He received 10 skin graft operations over a period of 3 months. The cost of the operations was \u20ac561,000 and was covered by medical insurance.\n<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QBL49WXgBXI&t=226s|title=Stromschlag beim Sprayen: Das Model und die Graffiti-Szene|date=8 December 2013|work=Der Spiegel|access-date=16 January 2020}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.spiegel.de/international/germany/graffiti-accidents-not-enough-to-put-sprayers-off-their-tag-addiction-a-936930.html|title=When Graffiti Becomes a Dangerous Addiction|last=Schrep|first=Bruno|date=2 December 2013|work=Spiegel Online|access-date=28 December 2019}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.cosmopolitan.com/style-beauty/fashion/a53143/julius-model-burn-scars/|title=90 Percent of This Model's Body Was Burned, but He Kept Working|last=Manning|first=Charles|date=5 February 2016|work=Cosmopolitan|access-date=16 January 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{dts|25 September 2014}}\n|Germany - Hamburg\n|Hit by train\n|64\n|[[:de:Oz (Sprayer)|Walter Josef Fischer]], 64, who went by the tag \"Oz\", was on the train tracks in between Hamburg Hauptbahnhof and Berliner Tor train stations. He was hit by a passing [[:de:S-Bahn|S-Bahn]] train. The cover of a power cable had newly sprayed graffiti on it. His backpack contained spray cans inside it.\n<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.spiegel.de/kultur/gesellschaft/oz-graffiti-sprayer-walter-josef-fischer-ist-tot-a-993963.html|title=At the death of the Sprayer OZ resistance to the monotony of everyday life|date=26 September 2014|work=Spiegel Online|access-date=24 August 2019}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.ndr.de/nachrichten/hamburg/Sprayer-Oz-bei-Unfall-ums-Leben-gekommen,oz116.html|title=Sprayer \"Oz\" died in an acci