 train carriages at a train depot. A 19-year-old person was with him acting as a lookout. He climbed onto one of the carriages, raised his hand, was electrocuted by overhead electrical wires and killed. \n<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.abc.net.au/news/2014-11-02/trespasser-electrocuted-in-brisbane-railway-yard/5860482|title=Brisbane railway yard electrocution: 26yo trespasser dies after graffiti attempt on train carriages|last=Watson|first=Matt|date=3 November 2014|work=ABC News(Australia)|access-date=28 December 2019}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.abc.net.au/news/2015-01-08/teen-trespass-tennyson-rail-yard-friend-electrocuted/6007108|title=Teen pleads guilty to trespass at Tennyson railway yard after friend's electrocution|last=Edwards|first=Alyse|date=8 January 2015|work=ABC News(Australia)|access-date=29 December 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{dts|07 December 2015}}\n|Portugal - Porto\n|Hit by train\n|18, 20, ?\n|Five people were at \u00c1guas Santas train station in Porto. When one of them barred the doors to the train to stop the train moving away, a passing train going 120km/h hit three of the five people, killing them. \n<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.publico.pt/2015/12/07/sociedade/noticia/tres-mortos-em-atropelamento-de-comboio-na-maia-1716777|title=Graffiti Death: \u201cJust by luck nothing like this ever happened\u201d|last=Cipriano|first=Carlos|date=7 December 2015|work=[[P\u00fablico (Portugal)]]|access-date=25 August 2019|last2=Henriques|first2=Ana|others=Grace Barbosa Ribeiro}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.publico.pt/2015/12/09/sociedade/noticia/identificados-dois-espanhois-que-se-ausentaram-apos-atropelamento-ferroviario-da-maia-1716881|title=Two Spaniards who were absent after Maia rail crash|author=Lusa|date=9 December 2015|website=P\u00fablico|language=Portuguese|access-date=25 August 2019}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.mirror.co.uk/news/world-news/graffiti-artists-dragged-deaths-trying-6977641|title=Graffiti artists dragged to deaths while trying to daub slogans on side of train as it pulled into station|last=Sobot|first=Rita|date=8 December 2015|work=Daily Mirror|access-date=25 August 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{dts|20 May 2016}}\n|Germany - M\u00f6nchengladbach\n|Hit by Train\n|29\n|A 29-year-old person was spraying graffiti on technical equipment near the train tracks when a freight train passed them. The force from the suction of the freight train threw them against the side of the train, killing them instantly. \n<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.spiegel.de/panorama/moenchengladbach-sprayer-wird-von-zug-erfasst-und-stirbt-a-1093352.html|title=sprayer is captured by Zug and dies|date=20 May 2016|work=Spiegel Online|access-date=1 January 2020}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.express.de/duesseldorf/moenchengladbach-todes-drama-um-graffiti-sprayer--29---von-zug-erfasst---tot-24092038|title=M\u00f6nchengladbach death drama about graffiti sprayer (29): captured by train - dead|date=20 May 2016|work=express.de|access-date=1 January 2020}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://bahnblogstelle.net/2016/05/20/vom-zug-erfasst-graffiti-sprayer-verunglueckt-auf-bahnanlage-in-moenchengladbach/|title=Vom Zug erfasst \u2013 Graffiti-Sprayer verungl\u00fcckt auf Bahnanlage in M\u00f6nchengladbach|date=20 May 2016|work=bahnblogstelle|access-date=1 January 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{dts|03 October 2016}}\n|Germany - Berlin\n|Hit by Train\n|18,19\n|Two people, aged 18 and 19, were hit by a train; a bag with spray utensils and spray paint cans were found nearby.\n<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.tagesspiegel.de/berlin/polizei-justiz/berlin-wilhelmsruh-zwei-graffiti-sprayer-von-s-bahn-ueberrollt-und-getoetet/14634642.html|title=Two graffiti sprayers run over by S-Bahn and killed|last=Hasselmann|first=Jorn|date=10 May 2016||work=Der Tagesspiegel|access-date=1 January 2020}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.bz-berlin.de/berlin/pankow/zwei-jugendliche-anscheinend-beim-sprayen-von-s-bahn-ueberfahren|title=Zwei Juge